abstract: New York Jets kickoff and kick return teams, under special-teams coordinator Mike Westhoff, are among the best in the league; running back Joe McKnight is averaging 45.6 yards per kick return, 11 yards more than anyone else in the NFL.
snippet: The Jets’ kickoff and kick return teams, under the special-teams coordinator Mike Westhoff, are among the best in the league.
lead_paragraph: The Jets’ kickoff and kick return teams, under the special-teams coordinator Mike Westhoff, are among the best in the league.

headline.main: For the Jets, Kickoffs and Returns, at Least, Have Not Been a Problem
